just sitting around in the base.)

Starscream

Starscream sneered at Reptillica. Over confidence will get him dead. 
Never under-estimate your opponent. This bot had alot to learn. 
Starscream waited for Zardus.
______________________________________________________________________
Brix/Fliq

"Let's hope so too," said Brix as he powers up the shuttle, "Let's go 
home." The words were taken to heart by Brix and Fliq, because after 
years of travelling around the galaxy, they finaly found a place 
where they belonged. A place they could call home.

"Let's go!"

Brix carefully lifted the ship off the ground, and they took off for 
Earth.
